_:N06d218839c5141c6b407cf341e3b6b59 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Andy has brought more than 30 years’ experience of working on major programmes when he joined Sellafield Ltd in June 2021.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously director for the Defence, Energy and Utilities arm of global consultancy and construction firm Mace, and was instrumental in the organisation expanding into the nuclear market, supporting new nuclear build and decommissioning in the UK.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
